Password validation:
Example 1-
password=input("pras@1997")
if password>"pras@1997":
    print("match")
else:
    print("Try Again")
print("Have a Good day")

Example 2-
password =("pras")
confirm_password=input()
if password==confirm_password:
    print("match")
else:
    print("Try again")
